ALTER PROCEDURE sapcrm.usp_roles_get_last_x_days (@InputDate DATE, @InputDays INT)
AS
BEGIN
    DECLARE @Date INT 
    DECLARE @DateBackDays INT
    --====================================================================================
    --SET DEFAULT IF NO PARAMETER - START
    --====================================================================================
    IF (@InputDate IS NULL)
       SET @Date = Convert(CHAR(8),GETDATE(),112);
       SET @DateBackDays = Convert(CHAR(8),DATEADD(DAY, -365, GETDATE()),112);
     --====================================================================================
    --SET DEFAULT IF NO PARAMETER - END
    --====================================================================================   
    IF (@InputDate IS NOT NULL)
       SET @Date = Convert(CHAR(8),@InputDate,112);
       SET @DateBackDays = Convert(CHAR(8),DATEADD(DAY, @InputDays, @InputDate),112);
    
    --PRINT @Date 
    --PRINT @DateBackDays 

	-- Drop the table if it already exists
    IF EXISTS ( SELECT * FROM sys.external_tables WHERE object_id = OBJECT_ID('sapcrm.ExternalCLOYFPROL2') )
        DROP EXTERNAL TABLE [sapcrm].[ExternalCLOYFPROL2]
    

    CREATE EXTERNAL TABLE sapcrm.ExternalCLOYFPROL2
        WITH (
            LOCATION = 'released/sapcrm/ExternalCLOYFPROL2/', 
            DATA_SOURCE = [zone-connected], --write location
            FILE_FORMAT = ParquetFormat
        )
    AS
    SELECT
    [0BPARTNER___T]
    ,[0BPROLE]
    ,[0BPROLE___T]
    ,[0BP_GROUP]
    ,[0BP_GROUP___T]
    ,[0CREATEDON]
    ,[FP_SOURCE]
    ,[FP_SOURCE___T]
    ,[0REQTSN]
    ,[0VALIDFROM]
    ,[0VALIDTO]
    ,[1ROWCOUNT]
    ,[0BP_CAT]
    ,[0BP_CAT___T]
    ,[0BP_GUID]
    ,[0BP_TYPE]
    ,[0BP_TYPE___T]
    ,[0FLGDELETED]
    ,[0INFOPROV]
    ,[0RECORDTP]
    FROM
        OPENROWSET(
            BULK 'sapcrm/CLOYFPROL2.parquet',
            DATA_SOURCE = 'sapcrm',
            FORMAT='PARQUET'
        ) AS CLOYFPROL2
    WHERE [0CREATEDON] between @DateBackDays AND @Date;


END

		Itinerary.[endLocation_externalNumber] AS vogntur_end_station_UIC,
		Itinerary.[endLocation_abbreviation] AS vogntur_end_station_fork,

		--Itinerary.[trainSection_beginDayOffset],
		--Itinerary.[BeginTimestamp] AS tog_start_timestamp,

		--Itinerary.[trainSection_endDayOffset],
		--Itinerary.[EndTimestamp] AS tog_end_timestamp,

		Itinerary.[location_externalNumber] AS station_aktuel_UIC,

		Itinerary.[Station_sequence] AS station_sekvens,

		--Itinerary.[itineraryStop_operationalArrivalDayOffset],
		--Itinerary.[ArrivalTimestamp],

		--Itinerary.[itineraryStop_operationalDepartureDayOffset],
		--Itinerary.[DepartureTimestamp],

		--Itinerary.[Station_from_externalNumber],

		VehicleTrip.[successor_departureTimetamp] AS post_afg_timestamp
	
	FROM
    	OPENROWSET(
	        BULK 'https://datalakegen2atlasdev.dfs.core.windows.net/zone-connected/IVU/FR_Itinerary.csv',
    	    FORMAT = 'CSV',
        	HEADER_ROW = TRUE,
        	FIELDTERMINATOR = ';',
	        PARSER_VERSION = '2.0'
    	) 
	WITH (
		[validity_validityDate] date,
		[trainGroup_externalNumber] bigint,
		[beginLocation_externalNumber] bigint,
		[beginLocation_abbreviation] nvarchar(4000) COLLATE Latin1_General_100_BIN2_UTF8,
		[endLocation_externalNumber] bigint,
		[endLocation_abbreviation] nvarchar(4000) COLLATE Latin1_General_100_BIN2_UTF8,
		[trainGroup_startDate] date,
		[trainSection_beginTime] time(0),
		[trainSection_beginDayOffset] bigint,
		[BeginTimestamp] datetime2(0),
		[trainSection_endTime] time(0),
		[trainSection_endDayOffset] bigint,
		[EndTimestamp] datetime2(0),
		[trainSection_distance] bigint,
		[location_externalNumber] bigint,
		[location_abbreviation] nvarchar(4000) COLLATE Latin1_General_100_BIN2_UTF8,
		[Station_sequence] bigint,
		[itineraryStop_operationalArrivalTime] time(0),
		--[itineraryStop_operationalArrivalDayOffset] bigint,
		--[ArrivalTimestamp] datetime2(0),
		[itineraryStop_operationalDepartureTime] time(0),
		--[itineraryStop_operationalDepartureDayOffset] bigint,
		--[DepartureTimestamp] datetime2(0),
		[Station_from] nvarchar(4000) COLLATE Latin1_General_100_BIN2_UTF8,
		[Station_from_externalNumber] bigint ,
		[Station_to] nvarchar(4000) COLLATE Latin1_General_100_BIN2_UTF8,
		[Station_to_externalNumber] bigint,
		[itineraryStop_distance] bigint,
		[itineraryStop_passthrough] bigint,
		[itineraryStop_track] nvarchar(4000),
		[itineraryStop_networkTrainNumber] bigint,
		[itineraryStop_trainCategory] nvarchar(4000),
		[Koereplan72timer] bigint,
		[SysValidFrom] datetime2(0),
		[SysValidTo] datetime2(0)
	)  AS Itinerary

    SELECT 
        TO_DATE(ACT_DATE, 'yyyyMMdd') AS activity_date, 
        CAST(LEFT(ACT_DATE,4) AS INT) AS activity_year, 
        CAST(SUBSTR(ACT_DATE, 5, 2) AS INT) AS activity_month,
        lma.CATEGORY AS category,
        IFNULL(PROC_TYPE___T, PROC_TYPE) AS process_type,
        SUM(lpk.TOTPOINTS) AS total_points    
    FROM loyalitet_medlemsaktivitet lma  
    INNER JOIN loyalitet_pointkontooperationer lpk ON lpk.MSH_GUID = lma.MENB_GUID
            AND lma.MEDL_GUID = lpk.ACTI_GUID
    WHERE lpk.0BPARTNER IS NOT NULL AND lma.ACT_DATE BETWEEN 20220131 AND 20220205 
    GROUP BY  
        lma.ACT_DATE,
        lma.CATEGORY,
        IFNULL(PROC_TYPE___T, PROC_TYPE)
    """)
